title: Five Guys Restaurant Locations 12.2007
name: Five Guys Restaurant Locations 12.2007
description:
Five Guys Famous Burgers and Fries is a fast casual restaurant chain that originated in the Washington D.C., metropolitan area. Started in 1986 in Arlington, Virginia the name originates from the owners having five sons. Five Guys sell burgers and fries and a few other items. The Restaurant has received many accolades including best burger awards.

This dataset displays all of the Five Guys Restaurant locations across the United States. The dataset contains the store's full physical address, phone, and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from fiveguys.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.

For more information, go to fiveguys.com

Data accessed on December 18, 2007

http://www.fiveguys.com/store_locator.aspx
